      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_87d302eab807a9c1e5f6e3c92b065d3a">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged by subject.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <bioghist id="aspace_18072c044bbd7d1cde5b290d0a89f642">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>The Yale Daily News was founded in 1878.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_aa15f99da21c49136beae9e2d4219f84">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of the constitution, correspondence, ledger, notes, and layout sheets documenting the activities and operations of the Yale Daily News.</p>  
